creator: Cox Media Group Inc.
descriptionHtml:
The ActionNewsJax.com news app offers a superior local news, weather and sports experience at home or on-the-go. You can count on ActionNewsJax.com WJAX/WFOX to provide the latest news, weather, sports and more for the Jacksonville, Florida metro area.

The ActionNewsJax.com news app offers the content you want most (top stories, weather and traffic) where you can get to it quickly and easily. Or, open the navigation to get in depth and in detail information. Get news for the metro Jacksonville and surrounding areas including LaVilla, Brooklyn, Southbank, San Marco, Riverside, Avondale, Five Points, Avondale, Riverside, Springfield, Eastside, San Marco, St. Nicholas, Ortega, Mandarin, Northside, Panama Park, Westside, Lake Shore, Murray Hill, New Town, Arlington, Palatka, St. Marys.

**********Features**********
¤ News, Weather, Sports, Traffic, Photos, Videos and More
¤ View Community/Neighborhood News
¤ Geo-located Weather and Advertising
¤ Interactive Radar
¤ Live Streaming Audio and Video of newscasts and live events
¤ Receive push alerts (notifications) regarding breaking news, breaking news, severe weather, school closings and more
¤ Set the size of the text to the size that is best for you
¤ Share Content via E-mail, Text Message and on Facebook and Twitter

**********Other Apps**********
Please also try our weather app (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.newssynergy.wtev&hl=en) to get automated voice delivery of weather alerts for your exact location. Location based Storm Alerts will signal three tones to direct you to the latest severe weather warnings. Under Tornado Watches and Warnings, the App streams live coverage of Channel 2 Action News and Severe Weather Team 2 tracking storms and giving out minute-by-minute information on specific streets and neighborhoods threatened by the storm.


Please note: This app features Nielsen’s proprietary measurement software which will allow you to contribute to market research, like Nielsen’s TV Ratings. Please see www.nielsen.com/digitalprivacy for more information.
descriptionShort: The ActionNewsJax.com news app provides news, weather & sports for Jacksonville

title: ActionNewsJax.com - News App

creator: Cox Media Group Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Action News Jax CBS47 & FOX30 is serving North-East Florida and South Georgia

Dig deeper on the major news of the day with our live and on-demand videos to keep you plugged in to what’s happening now.

Action News Jax is your guide to:


-
-
- Minute-by-minute weather using Action News Jax’s StormTracker Doppler Radar and 5-day Forecast so you know how the weather will impact you.
- Getting where you need to go on time with live drive times in and out of the Jacksonville Metro Area.
- Direct sports coverage of the Jacksonville Jaguars and more.
- Local news that matters for Duval, Nassau, St. Johns, Clay, Baker, Columbia, Putnam, Union, Bradford, Camden, Glynn, Brantley, Charlton, Ware and Pierce counties including Jacksonville, St. Augustine, Brunswick, Palatka, Lake City, and Starke.
- National and world news and what it means for you.
- Engaging content that you can share easily from the app to Twitter and Facebook.

Get accessible coverage that keeps you up-to-date with Action News Jax.

Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life. Please note: This app features Nielsen's proprietary measurement software, which will allow you to contribute to market research like Nielsen's TV Ratings. Please see www.nielsen.com/digitalprivacy for more information.
